67
00:05:25,304 --> 00:05:27,511
Yes, ma'am, whatever you say, ma'am!

68
00:05:27,504 --> 00:05:29,062
Huah! Leave it!

69
00:05:29,060 --> 00:05:32,382
So that's the hot house. Tour
continues this way, ladies, please.

70
00:05:32,375 --> 00:05:36,698
No dawdling. Um, so,
you know Jack pretty well, then?

71
00:05:36,692 --> 00:05:41,208
Oh, we were only together
for. . .a few days.

72
00:05:41,206 --> 00:05:42,935
But it was pretty intense.

73
00:05:44,283 --> 00:05:48,447
