78
00:06:00,669 --> 00:06:04,036
Oi, you talking about me?

79
00:06:04,025 --> 00:06:07,938
No, no, we were just discussing
alien flora, weren't we? Oh, yeah.

80
00:06:07,937 --> 00:06:11,100
